Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小田岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天你去剑道部拍的她们练习赛的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么只有在拍这个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为其他人没有拍得价值嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是对方的学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  你这是在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等身宣传板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拿这东西来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  如果你认识的话也给我介绍介绍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第14话\N小莉莉的决意和咀嚼的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有说要加入剑道部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次只是去观摩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加比赛也纯粹是为了凑足人数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心上高中后不参加任何活动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这样明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东  护具定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我有初中时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次记得带来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我在玩从学生那里没收的游戏机…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙好难打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被其他老师看到不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙要打下半身才有效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前玩过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为都是这个模式的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…被其他老师看到不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  轻松取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！我才不承认什么3D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏还是要2D才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sprite万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那下次要不要比一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？好啊  想用什么比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Famicom吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有过注释了…スーファミ：スーパーファミコン(Super Famicom)的简称，\N任天堂于1990年发行的游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  用MD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MD=MEGA DRIVE，SEGA产主机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确点说  用DUO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PCE-DUO：NEC产卡带光盘一体机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老师…你是爱好者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的学生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  老师你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葱粒…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东的称呼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难选择嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个怎么说来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意接踵而来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过推荐的还是最上面3个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得啊  小莉莉最好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  老师你觉得呢  哪个最好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的大会就4人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东她…的确很可惜  但是我不会让她参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小莉莉她很喜欢剑道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东同学她自己也乐在其中的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  乐在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  也不能强拉她进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出啥事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有干劲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  去社团活动咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天我值日  你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学  今天是你值日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  今天我有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托把我那份也做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说的那么直白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫…宫崎同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  就你一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…其他人都偷懒跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开小差啊…真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦  我们又不同班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次强拉你来练习赛对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引胴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…很开心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能考上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能参加部团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没什么集中力又很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多念书不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有没有参加部团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩都一样烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说  书念得好  部团活动也能得心应手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然再怎么用功也是白费吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太单纯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说都能骗她上船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样逼她…好愉快啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的成绩表  刚入学时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张  是之前考试的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进步了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我加入了剑道部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上高中后成绩退步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为课程越来越难…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错！是因为你没有继续练剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道能够锻炼精神以及集中力对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你放弃了  所以念书时的集中力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的…的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我男朋友开始算起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道部里成绩优秀的人非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便哪个都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入剑道部的话  也能让他们帮你念书咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！竟然有这么棒的特权…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是笨蛋还是迟钝给我说清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋的话念书也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝的话不就更要练剑道来集中精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对  对  对…对的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其拼小命把成绩硬提高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不努力精进拿手的剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后靠推荐上大学不是更好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要当笨蛋的话  也要做个剑道笨蛋呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（靠推荐上大学）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听见咚的一声？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一定要加入剑道部…才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加入！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我加入剑道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了！让我加入！让我加入！求你了！…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…看来挺容易使唤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我加入剑道部！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎小莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  东同学也要加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以参加5人的比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东聪莉的称呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小莉莉」不就行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  终于凑足五个人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  而且是很好的人才哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照那个阵容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大赛预选也值得人期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预选结束后  我们再比一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  不过说实话我是不打算输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也是我们轻松取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是另一间学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是不会那么简单就被打败的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  还要再赌点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…指导者来打赌不怎么好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖杯不是为了这种事情而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真要进军全国的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指导者也要认真考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想认真地去干而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是顾问该说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要短时间内锻炼她们的话  就进行合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在各种准备方面就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也变得像个剑道部的样子了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吗？9点以后的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊  你不认真做好顾问工作可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了因为考试不能参加的前辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全国大赛进军吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为部长的你不够强大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉不到部员的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间明明只有我和纪梨乃两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师为了我又鼓起干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球部的棒球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网球部的网球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橄榄球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任从3楼掉下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要寻找强者之时所遇到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后小都都也入部了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  和小鞘之间发生了点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那也不是什么难事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常地去和小鞘道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要道歉  是她不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘也打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中坚小鞘你上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不能加入剑道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实不喜欢剑道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就很喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…父母说上高中后就不能再练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也这么决定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是东的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  现在我不好好栽培她们怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发愁的话怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  现在可没时间闲玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周末就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大赛预选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大赛预选…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了别吓着！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次获胜之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是全国大赛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是IH大赛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能带你们打进全国大赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要学校能认可出众的我所筑建的实绩的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那怎么样都无所谓的蠢事就能一笔勾销了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用辞职也没事了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！你先在个人战拿下优胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把进军全国的资格抢下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  高中剑道还是要比团体赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体赛能够进军全国才是真正展现指导者实力的表现啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体赛打向全国！这才是我独一无二的生存之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜  有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有备用的  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你入部真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里人同意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母也很担心我自不参加部团后成绩下降的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  答应让我加入剑道部再试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老师也一同劝说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  很好啊  东
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不过  成绩退步的话还是非要退出不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩优秀组！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面就交给你们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会认真教你的啦  莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这样就聚齐5人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大赛上一定也能有出色的表现！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋斗吧！我的战士们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们男生还是一如既往地被忽略了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在个人战加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要进一步锻炼你们以及和东的团队合作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以本周末进行合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校方面已经批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像部团活动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子才有大赛气氛啊  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在哪里进行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:17:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在学校里连续两天的练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会彻底的锻炼你们  做好觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…合宿不能到山上呀海边呀瀑布呀寺院啦之类的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设备很齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少和其他学校一起练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没那个门路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就成了平日的练习了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  作为补偿  町户高的女生会一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町户高是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你前辈的学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  男生也会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生不会来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把男生也叫来就没裁判了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无视我们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉越来越正式了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君有合宿过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  中学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来小珠你是头一回？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然练习很严格  但晚上大家闹得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹得很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过男生只有两个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君又有小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  下个周末
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就麻烦您独自吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为是部团活动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿吗…在什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生也一起住在学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中田家的…那个…勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是那个勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和那个勇次君一起住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要搞错内容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,250元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:50.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这也不忘超剑战队的录像吗小珠！）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合…宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}透きとおる陽射しが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}みんなの背中輝いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}同じ日々目指してるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう寂しくならないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰もひとりぼっちじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心まで立ち止まる時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その笑顔でみんなが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}見守ってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから眩しさに飛びこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}青空に届く{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひるまずにひたすらに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この道を行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いつかときめきの頂点に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生まれるよ虹の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}苦しくて焦っても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}乗り越えられるきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}{\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}喜欢着纯净的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我们的背后都闪耀着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}每一日都朝着同一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就再也不会感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}谁也不会是孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}若是心中彷徨无法前进的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我会用这份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}把大家守护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}因此光彩夺目地展翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}那份力量直达蓝天之上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}毫不畏惧  毫不分心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}向着前程全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}直到心跳的顶点时分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就会绽放出彩虹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就算再多艰辛苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我也一定能越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}让我们共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}{\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
